## 3. Pre-launch checklist

Run through this in order **right before** flipping production traffic on.

### Secret rotation

The MLabs handoff rotates these from "MLabs-dev" values to "client-prod"
values. Both old and new must be valid simultaneously during handoff window
(typically 24h) to avoid breaking live sessions.

- [ ] **`BETTER_AUTH_SECRET`** rotated.
      Generate with `openssl rand -base64 32`. Update in `{{HOSTING_PROVIDER}}` secrets.
- [ ] **`POSTMARK_API_KEY`** rotated.
      Either transfer the Postmark Server (Postmark UI → Server Settings →
      Account → Transfer ownership) or create a new Server in the client's
      Postmark account and swap the token.
- [ ] **`DATABASE_URL`** rotated.
      Either transfer the Neon project (Neon UI → Settings → Transfer to
      Organization) or `pg_dump` + restore into a client-owned Neon project.
- [ ] **`REPLIT_OBJECT_STORAGE_BUCKET_ID`** — re-pointed at a client-owned
      bucket (see §6 below).
- [ ] All other env vars in `.env.example` reviewed for MLabs-specific values.

### Build-time gates

- [ ] `npm run verify:deeplinks -- https://{{PROD_HOST}}` — green.
- [ ] `npm run check-contrast` — green (WCAG AA across all token pairs).
- [ ] `npm run lint` — green.
- [ ] `npm run typecheck` — green (or only pre-existing waivers).
- [ ] `npm run test` — green.

### Mobile manual gates

- [ ] **Maestro suite** — 11 flows run locally against a production-built
      preview app (CONTRIBUTING.md has the runner). All green.
- [ ] iOS TestFlight build installed + smoke-tested by both MLabs and client.
- [ ] Android Internal Track build installed + smoke-tested.

### Web manual gates

- [ ] Sign-up → verify email → home flow walked end-to-end on prod.
- [ ] Password reset flow walked end-to-end on prod.
- [ ] Admin dashboard accessible to client's admin account.
- [ ] Sentry / log dashboard wired and reporting from prod (if applicable).

