## 6. Replit setup

Per `docs/handover/replit-setup.md`. Summary checklist:

- [ ] **Replit project ownership transferred** to client's Replit account.
      Replit UI → Project → Settings → Transfer ownership.
- [ ] **`.replit` deploy config** preserved (Reserved VM, not Autoscale —
      polling endpoints require warm instance per `docs/decisions/0002-polling-load.md`).
- [ ] **Object Storage bucket** created in the client's project.
      Tools → Object Storage → Create bucket. Copy bucket ID to
      `REPLIT_OBJECT_STORAGE_BUCKET_ID` in the client's secrets.
- [ ] **Custom domain** — set up at Replit UI → Domains → Connect domain
      ({{PROD_HOST}}). Wait for SSL provisioning (~5 min).
- [ ] **Deployment env vars** — all secrets from §3 copied into Replit's
      Secrets pane on the client's project (NOT the MLabs project).
- [ ] **Sleep / scaling policy** — Reserved VM Hacker tier is the default
      starting point; monitor and bump to Pro if peak traffic exceeds the
      polling math in `docs/decisions/0002-polling-load.md`.

