## 7. Post-handover responsibilities

What MLabs continues to own for `{{WARRANTY_DAYS}}` days after handover:

- Bug fixes against the merged spec
- One free secret-rotation if accidental exposure (`BETTER_AUTH_SECRET` etc.)
- 1h consult per week for client engineering questions

What MLabs does NOT own post-handover:

- New features
- Apple / Google account renewals (client owns)
- Server scaling / cost management (client owns)
- Postmark deliverability incidents from client-generated traffic
- App Store rejection appeals for content reasons

